print.color
Class ColoredPrinterWIN

java.lang.Object
  print.PrinterTemplate
      print.color.ColoredPrinterTemplate
          print.color.ColoredPrinterWIN
All Implemented Interfaces:
ColoredPrinterI, PrinterI
public class ColoredPrinterWIN
extends ColoredPrinterTemplate

This class is an implementation of the Colored Printer interface. It works correctly on both UNIX terminal and WINDOWS command console. It implements all abstract methods inherited from the PrinterTemplate class. All output is sent to terminal using the PrintStream provided by AnsiConsole.out.

Version:
1.25 beta
Author:
Diogo Nunes
